ygData.messageBody:
Wait, amg all kochin kura wiz, I'm the only one with true ancient wiz
blood, hehe. My grandfather is a wizard, my father is a wizard, so are my
brothers.... ;)

Anyway, I try VZ for a short while, very sian hunting newbie mob again,
more sian that in Inno (which I can at least wander around with my teleport
spells). In the end go back Inno and camp for webclaw but cant find the
mob. So I swim from the gnoll camp around the whole lake exploring all
islands and isle, kinda fun, hehe.

Ziltus the wandering wizard
